                     <hi rend="largeCaps">WALTER REEVES</hi> (16)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18800112-171-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18800112-171-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18800112-171-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>, Unlawfully obtaining by false pretences from <persName id="t18800112-name-206" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18800112-name-206" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18800112-name-206" type="surname" value="SCHMID"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18800112-name-206" type="given" value="GERARD DE"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18800112-171-offence-1 t18800112-name-206"></join>Gerard de Schmid</persName> six tame fowls <hi rend="italic">other Counts</hi> for similar offences, and for conspiracy with others to commit the same.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18800112-name-207" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18800112-name-207" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18800112-name-207" type="surname" value="WILLIAMS"></interp>
