                        <interp inst="t18800112-name-210" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD FROST</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a clerk at the money Order Office of the general Post-office—I produce a post-office order for 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. dated the 12th June, 1879, From Mr. Wood, and signed R.W. Whitehead.</p>
